          <td rowspan="2"><img name="home_r2_c3" src="../../images/home_img/home_r2_c3.gif" width="17" height="242" border="0" alt=""></td>
          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">Interview Transcript: <a href="../../issue4/gao_xingjian/bio.php" class="link3">Gao Xingjian</a> in conversation with <a href="../../issue4/david_dabydeen/bio.php" class="link3">David Dabydeen</a> and <a href="../../issue4/jonathan_morley/bio.php" class="link3">Jonathan Morley</a> </td>
